OL,3,CPeston: PM hasn't decided to quit, or
OL,4,Cat least not yet, despite Trump's
OL,5,C'scoop'
OL,7,FDon't forget that Andy Burnham does
OL,8,Fnot actually become an MP until circa
OL,9,F2.30 tomorrow. And as far as I know,
OL,10,FBurnham and Starmer have not spoken
OL,11,Fyet.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
