PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782123503
OL,3,CPeston: PM hasn't decided to quit, or
OL,4,Cat least not yet, despite Trump's
OL,5,C'scoop'
OL,7,FAs for when Starmer would step down -
OL,8,Fand the competing options appear to be
OL,9,Frecess in mid July or late September -
OL,10,Fthe two of them cannot guarantee a
OL,11,Ftimetable for the formal transfer of
OL,12,Fpower even if they agree one, because
OL,13,Fany MP could in theory force a
OL,14,Fleadership contest by securing the
OL,15,Frequisite 81 nominations.
OL,17,FIn 2007, John McDonnell tried and
OL,18,Ffailed to upset the analogous apple
OL,19,Fcart, to prevent the coronation of
OL,20,FGordon Brown in succession to Tony
OL,21,FBlair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
