PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782123503
OL,3,CPeston: PM hasn't decided to quit, or
OL,4,Cat least not yet, despite Trump's
OL,5,C'scoop'
OL,7,FIt seems unlikely that Wes Streeting,
OL,8,Ffor example, would force a contest if
OL,9,FBurnham offers him a plum job (the
OL,10,Fpost of Chancellor is rumoured).
OL,12,FBut you never know with MPs - they are
OL,13,Fhuman after all - and Streeting or
OL,14,Fsomeone might just fancy having a go.
OL,16,FThere are some for example who share
OL,17,Fmy sister's characterisation of what's
OL,18,Fhappening as "man goes down the pub,
OL,19,Fbuys a round of drinks and wakes up in
OL,20,F10 Downing Street".
OL,26,@zD@NOU|D@RO]
